            p.section-1-block-text While most people enjoy casino gambling,
          .section-1-block-item
            img(src="./assets/icon2.svg", alt="icon-2").icons
            h4.section-1-block-title Design surveys
            p.section-1-block-text Sports betting, lottery and bingo playing for the fun
          .section-1-block-item
            img(src="./assets/icon3.svg", alt="icon-3").icons
